#1 cause of death for   children   are motor vehicles. Should we ban cars?#2 is drowning. Should we ban swimming pools? Going to the beach?#3 is fires/burning. Should we ban fire? Smoking? Defective heaters? Fireplaces?#4 is suffocation. Should we strap on scuba tanks to all children?#9 is death from falling. Should we make our   kids   wear nerf suits from head to toe?#11 is poisoning. Should we be required to watch everything our kids ingest, every minute, of every day, everywhere they may go?How about leaving   guns   alone, which is #12 on the list, until you're successful with all those others?